      <title>安全消息人士告訴路透社，無人機從伊朗方向飛越伊拉克蘇萊曼尼亞</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/drones-seen-flying-direction-iran-over-iraqs-sulaymaniya-security-sources-tell-2024-04-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三名安全消息人士週六告訴路透社，多架無人機從伊朗方向飛過伊拉克蘇萊曼尼亞省。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/drones-seen-flying-direction-iran-over-iraqs-sulaymaniya-security-sources-tell-2024-04-13/</guid>
