      <title>以色列稱伊朗向其發射無人機齊射，防空系統已做好準備</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/israel-says-iran-launched-drone-salvo-it-air-defences-poised-2024-04-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列週六表示，伊朗無人駕駛飛機已向以色列發射，防禦系統已準備好將其擊落，或拉響警報，命令任何受威脅地區的居民避難。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/israel-says-iran-launched-drone-salvo-it-air-defences-poised-2024-04-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 20:18:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
