      <title>哈馬斯拒絕以色列的停火反應，堅持主要要求</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/hamas-rejects-israels-ceasefire-response-sticks-main-demands-2024-04-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴勒斯坦伊斯蘭組織哈馬斯拒絕了以色列的停火提議，週六表示，它已向埃及和卡達的調解人提交了對上週一收到的提議的回應。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/hamas-rejects-israels-ceasefire-response-sticks-main-demands-2024-04-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 20:11:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>官方媒體稱約旦將暫時關閉領空</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/jordan-temporarily-close-airspace-state-media-says-2024-04-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[約旦將從晚上 11 點開始暫時關閉領空數小時。國有的 Al Mamlaka 新聞週六稱，（2000 GMT）所有進港、離港和過境飛機均已收到通知。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/jordan-temporarily-close-airspace-state-media-says-2024-04-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 19:30:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加薩人質陷入僵局，以色列人集會反對政府</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/israelis-rally-against-government-amid-deadlock-gaza-hostages-2024-04-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[週六，數千名以色列人舉行集會反對政府，有些人要求總理本雅明·內塔尼亞胡(Benjamin Netanyahu)取消長達半年的加薩戰爭，因為解救哈馬斯扣押在那裡的人質的外交努力陷入僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/israelis-rally-against-government-amid-deadlock-gaza-hostages-2024-04-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 19:06:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
