      <title>南非召回在六個非洲國家銷售的強生止咳糖漿，原因是疑似有毒</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/south-africa-recalls-jjs-cough-syrup-sold-six-african-nations-after-suspected-2024-04-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非衛生監管機構週六表示，正在召回多批強生公司產品。強生兒童止咳糖漿經檢測二甘醇含量超標。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/south-africa-recalls-jjs-cough-syrup-sold-six-african-nations-after-suspected-2024-04-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 18:50:00 GMT</pubDate>
